, "id": "15738602"}]}, "text": "\u201eNoch ist #Russland Systemgegner und ernsthafte milit\u00e4rische Bedrohung f\u00fcr #Europa. Aber in der l\u00e4ngeren Perspektive m\u00fcssen wir Russland wieder als europ\u00e4isches Land begreifen, das sich an der politischen Ordnung Europas aktiv und friedlich beteiligen kann.\u201c (tm) @WELTAMSONNTAG", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 39, "reply_count": 89, "like_count": 565, "quote_count": 10}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-02-20T09:35:40.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1495331306514825223", "id": "1495331306514825223", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 67, "end": 75, "tag": "Ukraine"}], "urls": [{"start": 257, "end": 280, "url": "https://t.co/gqkBNeikmE", "expanded_url": "https://www.welt.de/politik/deutschland/plus236994157/Merz-In-der-laengeren-Perspektive-Russland-wieder-als-europaeisches-Land-begreifen.html", "display_url": "welt.de/politik/deutsc\u2026"}]}, "text": "\u201ePutin will einen Konflikt mit der NATO herbeif\u00fchren, indem er die #Ukraine schon auf dem Weg in die NATO sieht. Dieser Erz\u00e4hlung d\u00fcrfen wir nicht folgen. Es handelt sich um einen Konflikt zwischen zwei gro\u00dfen europ\u00e4ischen L\u00e4ndern au\u00dferhalb der NATO.\u201c (tm)\nhttps://t.co/gqkBNeikmE", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 49, "reply_count": 122, "like_count": 514, "quote_count": 22}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "88", "name": "Political Body", "description": "A section of a government, like The Supreme Court"}, "entity": {"id": "1016738021939351558", "name": "North Atlantic Treaty Organization", "description": "North Atlantic Treaty Organization"}}, {"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1484601166080081920", "name": "Russo-Ukrainian conflict"}}, {"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "864931126132985856", "name": "Vladimir Putin", "description": "President of Russia Vladimir Putin"}}, {"domain": {"id": "35", "name": "Politician", "description": "Politicians in the world, like Joe Biden"}, "entity": {"id": "864931126132985856", "name": "Vladimir Putin", "description": "President of Russia Vladimir Putin"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1494998684139929604"}], "created_at": "2022-02-19T18:08:38.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1495098014255534084", "id": "1495098014255534084", "text": "RT @HendrikWuest: Danke f\u00fcr Geschlossenheit, Teamgeist und Zusammenhalt! Danke f\u00fcr 99,1 Prozent! \ud83d\ude4fWir haben alle Chancen, unser Land noch b\u2026", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 50, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 16, "username": "HendrikWuest", "id": "724509927952277504"}]}, "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "replied_to", "id": "1495001439609016324"}], "created_at": "2022-02-19T11:44:54.000Z", "in_reply_to_user_id": "1059395748289232896", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1495001439609016324", "id": "1495001441219616771", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 39, "end": 52, "tag": "Erneuerbaren"}, {"start": 255, "end": 264, "tag": "MerzMail"}]}, "text": "\u201eDie Behauptung, schon heute w\u00e4ren die #Erneuerbaren billiger als alle anderen Energiequellen, h\u00e4lt einer \u00dcberpr\u00fcfung nicht stand. Das Gegenteil ist richtig, gerade f\u00fcr Windenergie werden in Deutschland immer noch die h\u00f6chsten Subventionen gezahlt.\u201c (tm) #MerzMail", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 128, "reply_count": 523, "like_count": 1250, "quote_count": 79}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-02-19T11:44:53.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1495001439609016324", "id": "1495001439609016324", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 269, "end": 278, "tag": "MerzMail"}]}, "text": "\u201eWir laufen in der Energiepolitik Gefahr, den Fehler des Jahres 2011 zu wiederholen: Bevor Alternativen wirklich zur Verf\u00fcgung stehen, werden preisg\u00fcnstige Energien verboten, wie bei der Kernenergie, oder weiter k\u00fcnstlich verteuert, wie die fossilen Brennstoffe.\u201c (tm) #MerzMail", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 246, "reply_count": 979, "like_count": 2391, "quote_count": 179}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-02-18T08:45:10.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1494593824710090753", "id": "1494593824710090753", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 61, "end": 68, "tag": "Illner"}, {"start": 79, "end": 89, "tag": "Inflation"}, {"start": 104, "end": 109, "tag": "Merz"}], "mentions": [{"start": 117, "end": 121, "username": "ZDF", "id": "57350105"}], "urls": [{"start": 146, "end": 169, "url": "https://t.co/98pL2Fxe1j", "expanded_url": "https://www.zdf.de/politik/maybrit-illner/preis-schock-nach-der-pandemie-wohlstand-in-gefahr-mit-lindner-und-merz-ua-maybrit-illner-vom-17-februar-2022-100.html", "display_url": "zdf.de/politik/maybri\u2026"}]}, "text": "Sendung verpasst? Hier k\u00f6nnen Sie die Diskussion bei Maybrit #Illner zum Thema #Inflation mit Friedrich #Merz in der @ZDF-Mediathek ansehen. (tm)\nhttps://t.co/98pL2Fxe1j", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 18, "reply_count": 52, "like_count": 134, "quote_count": 3}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "67", "name": "Interests and Hobbies", "description": "Interests, opinions, and behaviors of individuals, groups, or cultures; like Speciality Cooking or Theme Parks"}, "entity": {"id": "1486458201117642754", "name": "Inflation"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-02-17T22:13:17.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1494434804296785926", "id": "1494434804296785926", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 195, "end": 212, "tag": "Elektromobilit\u00e4t"}], "mentions": [{"start": 19, "end": 30, "username": "tobiashans", "id": "19751955"}]}, "text": "\u201eMinisterpr\u00e4sident @tobiashans warnt zu Recht davor, durch heutige Fehler viele Arbeitspl\u00e4tze in Industrien zu gef\u00e4hrden, die wir in 20 Jahren noch dringend brauchen: Einseitige Fokussierung auf #Elektromobilit\u00e4t w\u00e4re ebenso falsch wie ein Verbot des Verbrennungsmotors.\u201c (tm)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 114, "reply_count": 430, "like_count": 1190, "quote_count": 58}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "45", "name": "Brand Vertical", "description": "Top level entities that describe a Brands industry"}, "entity": {"id": "781974597302226944", "name": "Transportation"}}, {"domain": {"id": "30", "name": "Entities [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service top level domain, every item that is in Entity Service should be in this domain"}, "entity": {"id": "848920371311001600", "name": "Technology", "description": "Technology and computing"}}, {"domain": {"id": "165", "name": "Technology", "description": "for individual and types of technology, e.g., food technology, 3D printing"}, "entity": {"id": "848920371311001600", "name": "Technology", "description": "Technology and computing"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-02-17T22:03:52.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1494432435379085314", "id": "1494432435379085314", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 58, "end": 66, "tag": "Energie"}, {"start": 273, "end": 280, "tag": "Illner"}]}, "text": "\u201eWenn man der Meinung ist, durch Verteuerung der fossilen #Energie auf andere Energietr\u00e4ger ausweichen zu wollen, sollten diese auch verf\u00fcgbar sein. Wir steigen aus allen m\u00f6glichen Formen der Energieerzeugung aus \u2013 aber Alternativen fehlen und der Netzausbau stockt.\u201c (tm) #Illner", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 152, "reply_count": 372, "like_count": 1521, "quote_count": 37}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-02-17T21:50:59.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1494429194129973253", "id": "1494429194129973253", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 1, "end": 11, "tag": "Inflation"}, {"start": 216, "end": 233, "tag": "Pendlerpauschale"}, {"start": 250, "end": 265, "tag": "Mehrwertsteuer"}]}, "text": "\u201e#Inflation trifft nicht nur sozial Schwache, sondern auch durchschnittlich verdienende Familien, die sich dann keinen Sommerurlaub mehr leisten k\u00f6nnen. Der Staat verdient an steigenden Energiepreisen, er k\u00f6nnte die #Pendlerpauschale erh\u00f6hen und die #Mehrwertsteuer senken.\u201c (tm)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 174, "reply_count": 663, "like_count": 1818, "quote_count": 78}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "67", "name": "Interests and Hobbies", "description": "Interests, opinions, and behaviors of individuals, groups, or cultures; like Speciality Cooking or Theme Parks"}, "entity": {"id": "1486458201117642754", "name": "Inflation"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-02-17T21:42:46.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1494427125251772420", "id": "1494427125251772420", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 11, "end": 21, "tag": "Inflation"}, {"start": 40, "end": 44, "tag": "EZB"}, {"start": 127, "end": 