welt: So sch\u00e4tzt @_FriedrichMerz die Gefahr eines Krieges in der Ukraine ein: https://t.co/ZsiquAqKBC", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 55, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 8, "username": "welt", "id": "8720562"}, {"start": 21, "end": 36, "username": "_FriedrichMerz", "id": "1059395748289232896"}], "urls": [{"start": 82, "end": 105, "url": "https://t.co/ZsiquAqKBC", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/welt/status/1488216441736286209/video/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/ZsiquAqKBC"}]}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-31T18:24:33.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488216650373550087", "id": "1488216650373550087", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 83, "end": 90, "tag": "Gr\u00fcnen"}], "mentions": [{"start": 274, "end": 279, "username": "welt", "id": "8720562"}], "urls": [{"start": 280, "end": 303, "url": "https://t.co/73qsxCsNfO", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1488216650373550087/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/73qsxCsNfO"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1488216628445732866"]}, "text": "\u201eWir steigen aus Kernenergie, Braunkohle und Steinkohle aus \u2013 und wenn es nach den #Gr\u00fcnen geht, so rasch wie m\u00f6glich auch aus dem Gas. Diese Rechnung wird nicht aufgehen. Die Elektrifizierung braucht Strom, den Deutschland nicht in ausreichender Menge erzeugen kann.\u201c (tm) @welt https://t.co/73qsxCsNfO", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 152, "reply_count": 382, "like_count": 1459, "quote_count": 30}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-31T18:15:39.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488214411001090048", "id": "1488214411001090048", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 1, "end": 10, "tag": "Russland"}, {"start": 48, "end": 56, "tag": "Ukraine"}], "mentions": [{"start": 265, "end": 270, "username": "welt", "id": "8720562"}]}, "text": "\u201e#Russland f\u00fchrt bereits seit 2014 Krieg in der #Ukraine und hat v\u00f6lkerrechtswidrig die Krim annektiert. Die Redensart \u201awenn geredet wird, wird nicht geschossen\u2018, ist also leider falsch \u2013 es wird seit Jahren fast jeden Tag geschossen und es sterben Menschen.\u201c (tm) @welt", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 129, "reply_count": 241, "like_count": 964, "quote_count": 33}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-31T18:04:48.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488211678722412552", "id": "1488211678722412552", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 5, "end": 14, "tag": "Pandemie"}, {"start": 219, "end": 226, "tag": "Corona"}], "mentions": [{"start": 272, "end": 277, "username": "welt", "id": "8720562"}]}, "text": "\u201eDie #Pandemie hinterl\u00e4sst vor allem bei Kindern und Jugendlichen immaterielle Sch\u00e4den. Wenn wir weiter \u00f6ffnen, sollten wir nicht bei Fu\u00dfballstadien, sondern bei Unis, Schulen und Kinderg\u00e4rten beginnen. Bei Kindern hat #Corona bisher keine gro\u00dfen Sch\u00e4den ausgel\u00f6st.\u201c (tm) @welt", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 249, "reply_count": 1827, "like_count": 2557, "quote_count": 379}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-31T17:46:45.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488207135871799296", "id": "1488207135871799296", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 40, "end": 47, "tag": "Corona"}, {"start": 73, "end": 85, "tag": "Impfpflicht"}], "mentions": [{"start": 273, "end": 278, "username": "welt", "id": "8720562"}]}, "text": "\u201eWir diskutieren nicht \u00fcber die jetzige #Corona-Welle, sondern \u00fcber eine #Impfpflicht f\u00fcr den Herbst. Die Unionsfraktion wird dazu wahrscheinlich in der n\u00e4chsten Sitzungswoche ein Eckpunktepapier vorlegen. Die entscheidende Frage bleibt aber: Wie wird das umgesetzt?\u201c (tm) @welt", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 72, "reply_count": 1626, "like_count": 397, "quote_count": 138}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-31T16:21:29.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488185679439974401", "id": "1488185679439974401", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 91, "end": 99, "tag": "Ukraine"}, {"start": 107, "end": 114, "tag": "Corona"}, {"start": 142, "end": 146, "tag": "CDU"}], "mentions": [{"start": 46, "end": 61, "username": "GoeringEckardt", "id": "626287930"}, {"start": 66, "end": 81, "username": "hendrikstreeck", "id": "1936091958"}, {"start": 185, "end": 190, "username": "welt", "id": "8720562"}]}, "text": "Ich freue mich darauf, heute Abend mit Katrin @GoeringEckardt und @hendrikstreeck \u00fcber die #Ukraine-Krise, #Corona und die Neuaufstellung der #CDU zu diskutieren. Um 18:35 Uhr live bei @welt, schauen Sie gerne mal rein! (FM)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 23, "reply_count": 127, "like_count": 312, "quote_count": 11}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-31T13:34:34.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488143673695035392", "id": "1488143673695035392", "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1488143635002634240"]}, "text": "\u201eIch danke allen Delegierten f\u00fcr das gro\u00dfe Vertrauen und freue mich auf die Arbeit hier im Konrad-Adenauer-Haus und in der Fraktion. Wir alle freuen uns darauf, unsere Aufgaben ab heute im Dienst des Landes zu erf\u00fcllen.\u201c (tm) https://t.co/USheUiKyjM", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 31, "reply_count": 46, "like_count": 456, "quote_count": 8}, "lang": "de", "entities": {"urls": [{"start": 226, "end": 249, "url": "https://t.co/USheUiKyjM", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1488143673695035392/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/USheUiKyjM"}]}}, {"created_at": "2022-01-31T13:17:08.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488139283085070338", "id": "1488139283085070338", "text": "\u201eMeine Freude heute ist getr\u00fcbt durch die Nachricht vom Tod zweier Polizeibeamter, die bei einem Routineeinsatz erschossen wurden. Den Familien und Angeh\u00f6rigen herzliches Beileid \u2013 und gro\u00dfen Dank allen Polizistinnen und Polizisten, die jeden Tag in unserem Land Dienst tun.\u201c (tm)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 87, "reply_count": 66, "like_count": 1419, "quote_count": 9}, "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1488136919703855105"}], "created_at": "2022-01-31T13:10:28.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488137609071185924", "id": "1488137609071185924", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 44, "end": 54, "tag": "Briefwahl"}, {"start": 93, "end": 101, "tag": "teamCDU"}], "mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 7, "username": "CDU", "id": "20429858"}, {"start": 56, "end": 71, "username": "_FriedrichMerz", "id": "1059395748289232896"}]}, "text": "RT @CDU: Jetzt auch amtlich best\u00e4tigt durch #Briefwahl: @_FriedrichMerz ist der neue Chef im #teamCDU (Ergebnis: 95,33 Prozent). An seiner\u2026", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 88, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "29", "name": "Events [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service related Events domain"}, "entity": {"id": "1439959177003089924", "name": "Bundestagswahl 2021"}}, {"domain": {"id": "38", "name": "Political Race", "description": ""}, "entity": {"id": "1439959177003089924", "name": "Bundestagswahl 2021"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1488135759513198595"}], "created_at": "2022-01-31T13:06:34.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1488136625934774273", "id": "1488136625934774273", "text": "RT @CDU: Jetzt live: Wir geben die Ergebnisse der Briefwahl zum Parteitag bekannt. Und dann packen wir den Neustart an \u2013 mit @_FriedrichMer\u2026", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 15, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 7, "username": "CDU", "id": "20429858"}]}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-29T19:21:20.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1487506162211819521", "id": "1487506162211819521", "text": "Herzlichen Gl\u00fcckwunsch an Omid @nouripour und @Ricarda_Lang zur Wahl als Vorsitzende von @Die_Gruenen. Auf einen fairen Wettbewerb! (FM)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 56, "reply_count": 513, "like_count": 1026, "quote_count": 70}, "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 31, "end": 41, "username": "nouripour", "id": "16674128"}, {"start": 46, "end": 59, "username": "Ricarda_Lang", "id": "1405886484"}, {"start": 89, "end": 101, "username": "Die_Gruenen", "id": "14553288"}]}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-28T10:02:34.000Z", "source": "Twitter Web App", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1487003158727602177", "id": "1487003158727602177", "text": "\u201eIch bin beim Parteitag wirklich \u00fcberw\u00e4ltigt gewesen von diesen 94,6 Prozent. Das ist eine Zahl, die h\u00e4tte ich mir nicht ertr\u00e4umt. Im ersten Moment konnte ich gar nicht sprechen.\u201c (tm)\nhttps://t.co/mAXnNWVSvg", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 28, "reply_count": 96, "like_count": 531, "quote_count": 5}, "lang": "de", "entities": {"urls": [{"start": 185, "end": 208, "url": "https://t.co/mAXnNWVSvg", "expanded_url": "https://www.rtl.de/cms/friedrich-merz-im-exklusiven-rtl-interview-so-emotional-erlebte-der-cdu-vorsitzende-seine-wahl-4907661.html", "display_url": "rtl.de/cms/friedrich-\u2026"}]}}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "replied_to", "id": "1486774810457821197"}], "created_at": "2022-01-27T18:55:12.000Z", "in_reply_to_user_id": "1059395748289232896", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1486774810457821197", "id": "1486774812093657096", "text": "Wir b\u00fcndeln damit die Arbeit in Partei und Fraktion. Ralph Brinkhaus bleibt aktives und wichtiges Mitglied unserer Bundestagsfraktion, ich werde seine F\u00e4higkeiten und seine Unterst\u00fctzung gern in Anspruch nehmen. (FM)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 33, "reply_count": 45, "like_count": 618, "quote_count": 4}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-27T18:55:12.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1486774810457821197", "id": "1486774810457821197", "text": "Auch wenn wir in der Sache unterschiedlicher Auffasung waren, so danke ich @rbrinkhaus f\u00fcr seine Bereitschaft, die beiden Aufgaben des Vorsitzenden in Partei und Fraktion in eine Hand zu legen. (FM)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 103, "reply_count": 160, "like_count": 1539, "quote_count": 24}, "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 75, "end": 86, "username": "rbrinkhaus", "id": "38001527"}]}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-27T17:53:45.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1486759346281275401", "id": "1486759346281275401", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 214, "end": 225, "tag": "WeRemember"}], "urls": [{"start": 226, "end": 249, "url": "https://t.co/XzI2pKmux4", "expanded_url": "https://youtu.be/aFkxrp3mg9s", "display_url": "youtu.be/aFkxrp3mg9s"}]}, "text": "\u201eEs erf\u00fcllt mich mit Beklemmung, am Jahrestag der Befreiung des Konzentrationslagers Auschwitz im Deutschen Bundestag \u00fcber die Frage reden zu m\u00fcssen, ob nicht m\u00f6glicherweise erneut ein Krieg in Europa droht.\u201c (tm) #WeRemember https://t.co/XzI2pKmux4", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 38, "reply_count": 64, "like_count": 437, "quote_count": 11}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "88", "name": "Political Body", "description": "A section of a government, like The Supreme Court"}, "entity": {"id": "1099777660912263168", "name": "German Bundestag", "description": "The Bundestag is the German federal parliament."}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-27T13:13:08.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1486688725769797632", "id": "1486688725769797632", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 226, "end": 237, "tag": "WeRemember"}], "urls": [{"start": 238, "end": 261, "url": "https://t.co/n2RhX9X9gm", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1486688725769797632/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/n2RhX9X9gm"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1486688721030336515"]}, "text": "\u201eDie Jungen sind nicht verantwortlich f\u00fcr das, was damals geschah. Aber sie sind verantwortlich f\u00fcr das, was in der Geschichte daraus wird.\u201c Dieses Wort von Richard von Weizs\u00e4cker vom 8. Mai 1985 gilt heute mehr denn je. (FM) #WeRemember https://t.co/n2RhX9X9gm", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 112, "reply_count": 116, "like_count": 1368, "quote_count": 14}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-26T19:03:24.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1486414486219206661", "id": "1486414486219206661", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 80, "end": 88, "tag": "Ukraine"}], "mentions": [{"start": 49, "end": 62, "username": "MelnykAndrij", "id": "2959037001"}], "urls": [{"start": 95, "end": 118, "url": "https://t.co/ej3PYlsZ6a", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1486414486219206661/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/ej3PYlsZ6a"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1486414482297565192"]}, "text": "Heute im Bundestag: Wichtiger Austausch mit S.E. @MelnykAndrij, Botschafter der #Ukraine. (tm) https://t.co/ej3PYlsZ6a", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 38, "reply_count": 68, "like_count": 654, "quote_count": 6}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "88", "name": "Political Body", "description": "A section of a government, like The Supreme Court"}, "entity": {"id": "1099777660912263168", "name": "German Bundestag", "description": "The Bundestag is the German federal parliament."}}], "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1486252072999825416"}], "created_at": "2022-01-26T08:40:15.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1486257664216739841", "id": "