entions": [{"start": 75, "end": 86, "username": "rbrinkhaus", "id": "38001527"}]}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-26T08:18:02.000Z", "source": "Twitter Media Studio", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "20429858", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1486252072999825416", "id": "1486252072999825416", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 4, "end": 10, "tag": "Ampel"}, {"start": 226, "end": 235, "tag": "Merzrede"}, {"start": 240, "end": 248, "tag": "cdupt22"}], "mentions": [{"start": 60, "end": 75, "username": "_FriedrichMerz", "id": "1059395748289232896"}], "urls": [{"start": 250, "end": 273, "url": "https://t.co/EhztZwSrCo", "expanded_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ydduWyChWHE&list=PL7tW3uw1tajqsPFAp5mR4jfzyPJGm9hEB&index=2", "display_url": "youtube.com/watch?v=ydduWy\u2026"}, {"start": 274, "end": 297, "url": "https://t.co/eunkbL13qe", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/CDU/status/1486252072999825416/video/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/eunkbL13qe"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["13_1486251614893715456"]}, "text": "Die #Ampel ist orientierungs- und f\u00fchrungslos. Klartext von @_FriedrichMerz: \u201eSie, Herr Scholz, haben gesagt: Wer bei mir F\u00fchrung bestellt, bekommt auch F\u00fchrung. Unsere Frage ist: welche F\u00fchrung meinen Sie denn?\u201c \ud83d\udc49\ud83c\udffc Die ganze #Merzrede vom #cdupt22: https://t.co/EhztZwSrCo https://t.co/eunkbL13qe", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 115, "reply_count": 144, "like_count": 693, "quote_count": 17}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-25T12:35:35.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "115666099", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1485954500770910210", "id": "1485954500770910210", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 22, "end": 27, "tag": "Otte"}, {"start": 112, "end": 118, "tag": "noafd"}], "mentions": [{"start": 197, "end": 201, "username": "CDU", "id": "20429858"}, {"start": 245, "end": 257, "username": "PaulZiemiak", "id": "288696645"}]}, "text": "Wir fordern Herrn Dr. #Otte auf, die CDU sofort zu verlassen! \nWer als Christdemokrat \u00fcberhaupt erw\u00e4gt, von der #noafd f\u00fcr das Amt des Bundespr\u00e4sidenten nominiert zu werden, verletzt die Werte der @CDU und hat in unserer Partei nichts verloren. @PaulZiemiak", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 217, "reply_count": 666, "like_count": 2389, "quote_count": 74}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "29", "name": "Events [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service related Events domain"}, "entity": {"id": "1439959177003089924", "name": "Bundestagswahl 2021"}}, {"domain": {"id": "38", "name": "Political Race", "description": ""}, "entity": {"id": "1439959177003089924", "name": "Bundestagswahl 2021"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-22T11:14:18.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "793778228", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1484846884015550464", "id": "1484846884015550464", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 66, "end": 70, "tag": "CDU"}, {"start": 256, "end": 264, "tag": "cdupt22"}], "mentions": [{"start": 23, "end": 38, "username": "_FriedrichMerz", "id": "1059395748289232896"}, {"start": 86, "end": 90, "username": "CDU", "id": "20429858"}, {"start": 95, "end": 99, "username": "CSU", "id": "21107582"}], "urls": [{"start": 265, "end": 288, "url": "https://t.co/CoNpaD9cc1", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/Markus_Soeder/status/1484846884015550464/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/CoNpaD9cc1"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1484846878286135296"]}, "text": "Herzlichen Gl\u00fcckwunsch @_FriedrichMerz zur \u00fcberzeugenden Wahl zum #CDU-Vorsitzenden! \n@CDU und @CSU sind ein Team. Wir werden uns sehr gut abstimmen. Uns ist klar: 2021 soll sich nicht wiederholen. Wir wissen, dass wir nur durch Unterhaken st\u00e4rker werden. #cdupt22 https://t.co/CoNpaD9cc1", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 50, "reply_count": 268, "like_count": 631, "quote_count": 36}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "887779778912165888", "name": "Markus S\u00f6der", "description": "Markus S\u00f6der"}}, {"domain": {"id": "35", "name": "Politician", "description": "Politicians in the world, like Joe Biden"}, "entity": {"id": "887779778912165888", "name": "Markus S\u00f6der", "description": "Markus S\u00f6der"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-22T11:51:08.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "115666099", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1484856150856245251", "id": "1484856150856245251", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 249, "end": 257, "tag": "teamCDU"}, {"start": 258, "end": 267, "tag": "cdubpt22"}], "mentions": [{"start": 147, "end": 162, "username": "_FriedrichMerz", "id": "1059395748289232896"}]}, "text": "Herzlichen Dank f\u00fcr das Vertrauen! Die Aufgabe als Generalsekret\u00e4r erf\u00fcllt mich mit Ehre und Demut. Ich freue mich auf die Arbeit im Team, das von @_FriedrichMerz gef\u00fchrt wird. Gemeinsam k\u00e4mpfen wir f\u00fcr den Aufbruch und das Wiedererstarken der CDU. #teamCDU #cdubpt22", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 45, "reply_count": 132, "like_count": 1018, "quote_count": 11}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-22T10:57:50.000Z", "source": "Twitter Web App", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "20429858", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1484842738575106056", "id": "1484842738575106056", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "tag": "merzrede"}, {"start": 140, "end": 150, "tag": "eineUnion"}, {"start": 151, "end": 159, "tag": "teamCDU"}, {"start": 160, "end": 168, "tag": "cdupt22"}]}, "text": "#merzrede: Was wir im Jahr 2021 in der Union erlebt haben, darf sich nicht wiederholen und ich verspreche: Das wird sich nicht wiederholen.\n#eineUnion #teamCDU #cdupt22", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 19, "reply_count": 54, "like_count": 237, "quote_count": 3}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-19T13:08:30.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1483788459865165825", "id": "1483788459865165825", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 96, "end": 100, "tag": "CDU"}], "mentions": [{"start": 9, "end": 21, "username": "Junge_Union", "id": "17005237"}], "urls": [{"start": 281, "end": 304, "url": "https://t.co/bcjYr1nbA8", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1483788459865165825/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/bcjYr1nbA8"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1483788453619937283"]}, "text": "75 Jahre @Junge_Union sind 75 Jahre erfolgreiche Arbeit und Vertretung der jungen Generation in #CDU und CSU. Ich verbinde mit diesem Geburtstag dankbare Erinnerungen an den Beginn meiner politischen Arbeit vor \u00fcber 50 Jahren als JU-Vorsitzender in meiner Heimatstadt Brilon. (FM) https://t.co/bcjYr1nbA8", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 29, "reply_count": 116, "like_count": 390, "quote_count": 23}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-18T08:16:10.000Z", "source": "Twitter Web App", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1483352502926036992", "id": "1483352502926036992", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 58, "end": 68, "tag": "Inflation"}, {"start": 145, "end": 152, "tag": "Europa"}, {"start": 195, "end": 199, "tag": "EZB"}], "urls": [{"start": 257, "end": 280, "url": "https://t.co/cvAq2DQZdC", "expanded_url": "https://www.sueddeutsche.de/politik/friedrich-merz-ezb-inflation-1.5509721", "display_url": "sueddeutsche.de/politik/friedr\u2026"}]}, "text": "\u201eDie Anzeichen daf\u00fcr, dass wir auch 2022 eine beachtliche #Inflation haben werden, nehmen zu. Deswegen reagieren die USA und fast alle L\u00e4nder in #Europa, die nicht zum Euro-Raum geh\u00f6ren. Nur die #EZB reagiert nicht. Ich erwarte, dass sich das \u00e4ndert.\u201c (tm) https://t.co/cvAq2DQZdC", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 94, "reply_count": 114, "like_count": 819, "quote_count": 13}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2022-01-18T07:03:00.000Z", "source": "Twitter Media Studio", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "20429858", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1483334088119390208", "id": "1483334088119390208", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 15, "end": 23, "tag": "cdupt22"}, {"start": 79, "end": 90, "tag": "CDUVorsitz"}, {"start": 133, "end": 148, "tag": "Bundesvorstand"}, {"start": 238, "end": 246, "tag": "teamCDU"}], "mentions": [{"start": 36, "end": 51, "username": "_FriedrichMerz", "id": "1059395748289232896"}], "urls": [{"start": 250, "end": 273, "url": "https://t.co/laWGmCYDH6", "expanded_url": "https://www.cdu-parteitag.de/kandidaten", "display_url": "cdu-parteitag.de/kandidaten"}, {"start": 274, "end": 297, "url": "https://t.co/xFeXrYU8v7", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/CDU/status/1483334088119390208/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/xFeXrYU8v7"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1483154643756765196"]}, "text": "Am Samstag ist #cdupt22: Dann steht @_FriedrichMerz offiziell zur Wahl f\u00fcr den #CDUVorsitz. Und mit ihm viele neue K\u00f6pfe f\u00fcr den CDU-#Bundesvorstand. \u203c\ufe0f NEU: Auf unserer Parteitagsseite gibt es jetzt die ersten Vorstellungsvideos f\u00fcr das #teamCDU. \ud83d\udc49 https://t.co/laWGmCYDH6 https://t.co/xFeXrYU8v7", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 40, "reply_count": 100, "like_count": 207, "quote_count": 10}, "lang": "de"}], "places": [{"full_name": "Berlin, Deutschland", "name": "Berlin", "country": "Deutschland", "id": "3078869807f9dd36", "country_code": "DE", "geo": {"type": "Feature", "bbox": [13.088304, 52.338079, 13.760909, 52.675323], "properties": {}}, "place_type": "city"}]}, "meta": {"newest_id": "1497888150231859200", "oldest_id": "1482300343035875336", "result_count": 100, "next_token": "b26v89c19zqg8o3fpe45yfm031yu4djrm6wyxl1i6vqm5"}}}
{"http_status": 200, "account_name": "_FriedrichMerz", "account_data": {"Name": "Merz, Friedrich", "Partei": "CDU", "id": 1059395748289232896, "screen_name": "_FriedrichMerz", "t0": "20211020-103923.json", "value": "Merz, Friedrich"}, "params": [["query", "from:_FriedrichMerz"], ["max_results", "100"], ["start_time", "2007-01-01T00:00:00Z"], ["end_time", "2022-04-18T11:59:59Z"], ["tweet.fields", "attachments,author_id,context_annotations,conversation_id,created_at,entities,geo,id,in_reply_to_user_id,lang,possibly_sensitive,public_metrics,referenced_tweets,reply_settings,source,text,withheld"], ["expansions", "author_id,referenced_tweets.id,referenced_tweets.id.author_id,entities.mentions.username,attachments.poll_ids,attachments.media_keys,in_reply_to_user_id,geo.place_id"], ["media.fields", "duration_ms,height,media_key,preview_image_url,public_metrics,type,url,width"], ["place.fields", "contained_within,country,country_code,full_name,geo,id,name,place_type"], ["poll.fields", "duration_minutes,end_datetime,id,options,voting_status"], ["user.fields", "created_at,description,entities,id,location,name,pinned_tweet_id,profile_image_url,protected,public_metrics,url,username,verified,withheld"], ["next_token", "b26v89c19zqg8o3fpe45yfm031yu4djrm6wyxl1i6vqm5"]], "response": {"data": [{"text": "\u201eWir wollen 2022 nicht nur vier Landtagswahlen erfolgreich bestehen, sondern uns auch neu aufstellen und beweisen, dass zumindest eine Volkspartei noch eine Zukunft hat. Auf diese Arbeit freue ich mich. Der Weg wird nicht einfach, aber es lohnt sich, ihn zu gehen.\u201c (tm) #MerzMail", "conversation_id": "1479433679562752003", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 271, "end": 280, "tag": "MerzMail"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 74, "reply_count": 559, "like_count": 1009, "quote_count": 35}, "created_at": "2022-01-07T12:44:10.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1479433679562752003", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck"}, {"entities": {"urls": [{"start": 83, "end": 106, "url": "https://t.co/FAOvREbuNW", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1478020992706482180/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/FAOvREbuNW"}], "mentions": [{"start": 36, "end": 50, "username": "Markus_Soeder", "id": "793778228"}]}, "text": "Gutes Gespr\u00e4ch zum Jahresbeginn mit @Markus_Soeder am Kirchsee in Oberbayern. (FM) https://t.co/FAOvREbuNW", "conversation_id": "1478020992706482180", "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 77, "reply_count": 539, "like_count": 1422, "quote_count": 78}, "created_at": "2022-01-03T15:10:39.000Z", "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1478020723251851264"]}, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1478020992706482180", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck", "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "887779778912165888", "name": "Markus S\u00f6der", "description": "Markus S\u00f6der"}}, {"domain": {"id": "35", "name": "Politician", "description": "Politicians in the world, like Joe Biden"}, "entity": {"id": "887779778912165888", "name": "Markus S\u00f6der", "description": "Markus S\u00f6der"}}]}, {"text": "Ich w\u00fcnsche Ihnen und uns allen ein erfolgreiches Jahr 2022. Es wird ein gutes Jahr: weniger Corona und eine starke #CDU! Vor allem aber: bleiben Sie gesund und zuversichtlich. \n\nHerzlich,\nIhr Friedrich Merz", "conversation_id": "1477243433328775168", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 116, "end": 120, "tag": "CDU"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 88, "reply_count": 302, "like_count": 2164, "quote_count": 23}, "created_at": "2022-01-01T11:40:55.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1477243433328775168", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}]}, {"entities": {"urls": [{"start": 180, "end": 203, "url": "https://t.co/QixEZ2atOD", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1474071924519149569/video/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/QixEZ2atOD"}], "hashtags": [{"start": 50, "end": 62, "tag": "Weihnachten"}]}, "text": "Was war das f\u00fcr ein Jahr! Ich w\u00fcnsche Ihnen frohe #Weihnachten und einige besinnliche und ruhige Tage und einen guten Start in ein gesundes Jahr 2022!\n\nHerzlich\nIhr Friedrich Merz https://t.co/QixEZ2atOD", "conversation_id": "1474071924519149569", "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 75, "reply_count": 225, "like_count": 1271, "quote_count": 15}, "created_at": "2021-12-23T17:38:28.000Z", "attachments": {"media_keys": ["13_1474053924126658565"]}, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1474071924519149569", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "Twitter Media Studio"}, {"text": "RT @rtl_direkt: \u201eDas wird ein Kurs nicht nach links und nicht nach rechts sein, sondern nach vorne.\u201c @_FriedrichMerz im Talk mit @JanHofer\u2026", "conversation_id": "1473189811955675136", "reply_settings": "everyone", "referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1473043489499852800"}], "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 14, "username": "rtl_direkt", "id": "1423204991578296321"}, {"start": 101, "end": 116, "username": "_FriedrichMerz", "id": "1059395748289232896"}, {"start": 129, "end": 138, "username": "JanHofer", "id": "433303871"}]}, "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 16, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "created_at": "2021-12-21T07:13:16.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1473189811955675136", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "Twitter for iPhone"}, {"entities": {"urls": [{"start": 257, "end": 280, "url": "https://t.co/4ojCyXo0We", "expanded_url": "https://www.tagesschau.de/inland/innenpolitik/merz-cdu-vorsitzender-107.html", "display_url": "tagesschau.de/inland/innenpo\u2026"}], "hashtags": [{"start": 18, "end": 38, "tag": "Mitgliederbefragung"}, {"start": 55, "end": 59, "tag": "CDU"}]}, "text": "\u201eDas Ergebnis der #Mitgliederbefragung zeigt, dass die #CDU Erneuerung will. Wir werden eine moderne Volkspartei sein. Ich stelle sogar an uns selbst den Anspruch, die modernste Volkspartei Europas zu sein. Und das werde ich auch ganz konkret zeigen.\u201c (tm)\nhttps://t.co/4ojCyXo0We", "conversation_id": "1472959891631489025", "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 65, "reply_count": 361, "like_count": 686, "quote_count": 29}, "created_at": "2021-12-20T15:59:39.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1472959891631489025", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck"}, {"entities": {"urls": [{"start": 257, "end": 280, "url": "https://t.co/KqcMECHpyh", "expanded_url": "https://www.bild.de/bild-plus/politik/inland/politik-inland/merz-im-interview-lauterbach-neigt-zu-sehr-starken-uebertreibungen-78582010.bild.html", "display_url": "bild.de/bild-plus/poli\u2026", "unwound_url": "https://www.bild.de/bild-plus/politik/inland/politik-inland/merz-im-interview-lauterbach-neigt-zu-sehr-starken-uebertreibungen-78582010.bild.html"}], "hashtags": [{"start": 22, "end": 33, "tag": "Lauterbach"}, {"start": 223, "end": 232, "tag": "Pandemie"}]}, "text": "\u201eNiemand spricht Karl #Lauterbach die Fachkompetenz ab, aber er neigt leider zu sehr starken \u00dcbertreibungen. Er muss ein vern\u00fcnftiges Ma\u00df finden und vor allem den Menschen die Zuversicht vermitteln, dass wir irgendwann die #Pandemie hinter uns haben.\u201c (tm)\nhttps://t.co/KqcMECHpyh", "conversation_id": "1472533222886342661", "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 219, "reply_count": 1455, "like_count": 2415, "quote_count": 187}, "created_at": "2021-12-19T11:44:13.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1472533222886342661", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck"}, {"entities": {"urls": [{"start": 281, "end": 304, "url": "https://t.co/4WQUVg7k24", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1472237622428938247/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/4WQUVg7k24"}], "hashtags": [{"start": 37, "end": 41, "tag": "CDU"}, {"start": 86, "end": 106, "tag": "Mitgliederbefragung"}, {"start": 271, "end": 280, "tag": "MerzMail"}]}, "text": "\u201eDer Respekt vor den Delegierten des #CDU-Bundesparteitags gebietet es, das Votum der #Mitgliederbefragung erst als endg\u00fcltig anzusehen, wenn die Delegierten am 21./22. Januar entschieden haben. Erst dann k\u00f6nnen wir im neuen Bundesvorstand unsere Arbeit aufnehmen.\u201c (tm) #MerzMail https://t.co/4WQUVg7k24", "conversation_id": "1472237622428938247", "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 41, "reply_count": 130, "like_count": 660, "quote_count": 7}, "created_at": "2021-12-18T16:09:36.000Z", "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1472237555647225866"]}, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1472237622428938247", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck"}, {"text": "@janboehm @zdfmagazin Das sind ja ganz neue Perspektiven. \ud83d\ude09 (tm)", "conversation_id": "1471842263995195395", "reply_settings": "everyone", "referenced_tweets": [{"type": "replied_to", "id": "1471842263995195395"}], "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 9, "username": "janboehm", "id": "19072286"}, {"start": 10, "end": 21, "username": "zdfmagazin", "id": "1335048846"}]}, "in_reply_to_user_id": "19072286", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 8, "reply_count": 45, "like_count": 875, "quote_count": 1}, "created_at": "2021-12-17T16:50:09.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1471885439787274249", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "1275778208755900422", "name": "Jan Bohmermann", "description": "German comedian"}}, {"domain": {"id": "58", "name": "Entertainment Personality", "description": "An entertainment personality in the world, like Anderson Cooper or Miranda Sings"}, "entity": {"id": "1275778208755900422", "name": "Jan Bohmermann", "description": "German comedian"}}]}, {"entities": {"urls": [{"start": 161, "end": 184, "url": "https://t.co/ToCg6ea38l", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1471842024185860104/video/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/ToCg6ea38l"}], "hashtags": [{"start": 21, "end": 25, "tag": "CDU"}, {"start": 140, "end": 148, "tag": "TeamCDU"}, {"start": 149, "end": 160, "tag": "CDUVorsitz"}]}, "text": "Liebe Mitglieder der #CDU, herzlichen Dank f\u00fcr dieses \u00fcberw\u00e4ltigende Vertrauen, das Sie mir mit der Abstimmung entgegengebracht haben! (FM) #TeamCDU #CDUVorsitz https://t.co/ToCg6ea38l", "conversation_id": "1471842024185860104", "reply_settings": "everyone", "geo": {"place_id": "07d9e49e3f883002"}, "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 229, "reply_count": 772, "like_count": 2943, "quote_count": 109}, "created_at": "2021-12-17T13:57:38.000Z", "attachments": {"media_keys": ["7_1471841939121217537"]}, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1471842024185860104", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "Twitter for iPhone"}, {"entities": {"urls": [{"start": 156, "end": 179, "url": "https://t.co/98Mbbl9P7R", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1471808826840129540/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/98Mbbl9P7R"}], "hashtags": [{"start": 31, "end": 39, "tag": "TeamCDU"}, {"start": 113, "end": 133, "tag": "Mitgliederbefragung"}, {"start": 138, "end": 149, "tag": "CDUVorsitz"}]}, "text": "Gute Laune und Optimismus beim #TeamCDU. In weniger als 90 Minuten gibt es das Ergebnis des ersten Wahlgangs der #Mitgliederbefragung zum #CDUVorsitz. (tm) https://t.co/98Mbbl9P7R", "conversation_id": "1471808826840129540", "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 38, "reply_count": 219, "like_count": 795, "quote_count": 54}, "created_at": "2021-12-17T11:45:43.000Z", "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1471808634095034373"]}, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1471808826840129540", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck"}, {"text": "\u201eWir wissen schon, dass es bei der Mitgliederbefragung zum #CDUVorsitz eine sehr hohe Wahlbeteiligung gab \u2013 64% der Mitglieder haben abgestimmt. Das ist sensationell und gibt mir ein gewisses Ma\u00df an Zuversicht, dass #TeamCDU ein gutes Wahlergebnis haben wird.\u201c (tm) #Merz #Illner", "conversation_id": "1471606089229778955", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 59, "end": 70, "tag": "CDUVorsitz"}, {"start": 216, "end": 224, "tag": "TeamCDU"}, {"start": 266, "end": 271, "tag": "Merz"}, {"start": 272, "end": 279, "tag": "Illner"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 37, "reply_count": 55, "like_count": 561, "quote_count": 7}, "created_at": "2021-12-16T22:20:07.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1471606089229778955", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck"}, {"text": "\u201eWir haben in diesem Land inzwischen eine gewisse Entgrenzung, wie wir miteinander reden. Es ist wieder etwas mehr Respekt vor der Meinung anderer n\u00f6tig.\u201c (tm) #Merz #Illner", "conversation_id": "1471604923410403343", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 160, "end": 165, "tag": "Merz"}, {"start": 166, "end": 173, "tag": "Illner"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 89, "reply_count": 318, "like_count": 1318, "quote_count": 29}, "created_at": "2021-12-16T22:15:29.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1471604923410403343", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck"}, {"text": "\u201eIch habe einige Vorbehalte gegen die #Impfpflicht, weil sie ein sehr starker Freiheitseingriff ist. Au\u00dferdem stellt sich die Frage des Vollzugs: Wie will der Staat das denn durchsetzen oder kontrollieren? Da lauert vielleicht schon die n\u00e4chste Entt\u00e4uschung.\u201c (tm) #Merz #Illner", "conversation_id": "1471599519234203656", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 38, "end": 50, "tag": "Impfpflicht"}, {"start": 265, "end": 270, "tag": "Merz"}, {"start": 271, "end": 278, "tag": "Illner"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 141, "reply_count": 736, "like_count": 1694, "quote_count": 100}, "created_at": "2021-12-16T21:54:01.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1471599519234203656", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck"}, {"text": "\u201eDas Problem in diesem Land ist nicht fehlendes Geld, sondern dass Investitionen nicht schnell genug auf die Stra\u00dfe kommen. Die spannende Frage wird sein: Schafft die #Ampel eine Staats- und Verwaltungsmodernisierung, sodass es schnellere Entscheidungen gibt?\u201c (tm) #Merz #Illner", "conversation_id": "1471598043871039490", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 167, "end": 173, "tag": "Ampel"}, {"start": 266, "end": 271, "tag": "Merz"}, {"start": 272, "end": 279, "tag": "Illner"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 33, "reply_count": 125, "like_count": 361, "quote_count": 11}, "created_at": "2021-12-16T21:48:09.000Z", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "id": "1471598043871039490", "lang": "de", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck", "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "65", "name": "Interests and Hobbies Vertical", "description": "Top level interests and hobbies groupings, like Food or Travel"}, "entity": {"id": "781974596148793345", "name": "Business & finance"}}, {"domain": {"id": "66", "name": "Interests and Hobbies Category", "descr