d Abgaben in Europa.\u201c (tm) #Maischberger"}, {"context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "3", "name": "TV Shows", "description": "Television shows from around the world"}, "entity": {"id": "10029286155", "name": "Menschen bei Maischberger"}}], "created_at": "2021-09-22T21:19:03.000Z", "conversation_id": "1440787751578726402", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "lang": "de", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 53, "reply_count": 59, "like_count": 758, "quote_count": 3}, "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 259, "end": 272, "tag": "Maischberger"}, {"start": 273, "end": 278, "tag": "Merz"}]}, "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck", "id": "1440787751578726402", "text": "\u201eDie vollst\u00e4ndige Abschaffung des Solidarit\u00e4tszuschlags ist eine Frage des Respekts und der Fairness gegen\u00fcber all denjenigen, die 30 Jahre lang die Deutsche Einheit finanziert haben. Alles andere ist ein gebrochenes Versprechen des Steuergesetzgebers.\u201c (tm) #Maischberger #Merz"}, {"context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "3", "name": "TV Shows", "description": "Television shows from around the world"}, "entity": {"id": "10029286155", "name": "Menschen bei Maischberger"}}, {"domain": {"id": "29", "name": "Events [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service related Events domain"}, "entity": {"id": "1439959177003089924", "name": "Bundestagswahl 2021"}}, {"domain": {"id": "38", "name": "Political Race", "description": ""}, "entity": {"id": "1439959177003089924", "name": "Bundestagswahl 2021"}}], "created_at": "2021-09-22T21:16:44.000Z", "conversation_id": "1440787167865806852", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "lang": "de", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 28, "reply_count": 84, "like_count": 473, "quote_count": 10}, "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 62, "end": 66, "tag": "SPD"}, {"start": 266, "end": 279, "tag": "Maischberger"}]}, "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck", "id": "1440