e", "created_at": "2021-01-26T12:35:57.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 44, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "RT @PaulZiemiak: Die CDU bekennt sich klar zur #Schuldenbremse. Sie hat die Grundlage geschaffen, dass Deutschland in der Pandemie finanzie\u2026", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 47, "end": 62, "tag": "Schuldenbremse"}], "mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 15, "username": "PaulZiemiak", "id": "288696645"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1354045333270048768", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1354045333270048768", "referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1354037828028686346"}], "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-26T12:35:39.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 44, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "Herzlichen Gl\u00fcckwunsch, @ArminLaschet. Das ist ein starker Vertrauensbeweis. Viel Erfolg f\u00fcr uns alle! (FM)", "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1352648688749973506", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 24, "end": 37, "username": "ArminLaschet", "id": "835541664"}]}, "conversation_id": "1352648688749973506", "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-22T16:05:53.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 34, "reply_count": 217, "like_count": 998, "quote_count": 26}, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "RT @MIT_bund: Eine Woche nach dem #cdupt21 blickt der MIT-Bundesvorstand heute zur\u00fcck - aber vor allem nach vorn. Jetzt muss es gemeinsam u\u2026", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 34, "end": 42, "tag": "cdupt21"}], "mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 12, "username": "MIT_bund", "id": "119012291"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1352641347900104709", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1352641347900104709", "referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1352637266582253571"}], "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-22T15:36:42.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 14, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "Heute kehren Stil und Anstand zur\u00fcck in das Wei\u00dfe Haus. Die Demokratie in #Amerika ist wieder ein Beispiel f\u00fcr die Welt. M\u00f6gen @JoeBiden und @KamalaHarris Erfolg haben \u2013 f\u00fcr uns alle. (FM) @rponline #InaugurationDay", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 74, "end": 82, "tag": "Amerika"}, {"start": 199, "end": 215, "tag": "InaugurationDay"}], "mentions": [{"start": 127, "end": 136, "username": "JoeBiden", "id": "939091"}, {"start": 141, "end": 154, "username": "KamalaHarris", "id": "30354991"}, {"start": 189, "end": 198, "username": "rponline", "id": "15427879"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1351952646438060044", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1351952646438060044", "lang": "de", "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "875006493984149509", "name": "Kamala Harris", "description": "US Senator Kamala Harris (CA)"}}, {"domain": {"id": "29", "name": "Events [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service related Events domain"}, "entity": {"id": "1349062721677914112", "name": "Inauguration Day: Watch as Joe Biden and Kamala Harris are sworn into office"}}, {"domain": {"id": "35", "name": "Politician", "description": "Politicians in the world, like Joe Biden"}, "entity": {"id": "875006493984149509", "name": "Kamala Harris", "description": "US Senator Kamala Harris (CA)"}}, {"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "10040395078", "name": "Joe Biden", "description": "US President Joe Biden"}}, {"domain": {"id": "35", "name": "Politician", "description": "Politicians in the world, like Joe Biden"}, "entity": {"id": "10040395078", "name": "Joe Biden", "description": "US President Joe Biden"}}], "created_at": "2021-01-20T18:00:03.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 68, "reply_count": 584, "like_count": 1336, "quote_count": 85}, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "RT @robinalexander_: Merz reiht sich ein. In Brief an alle Mitglieder, der @welt vorliegt, bedauert er \"Irritationen um meine Person\" und v\u2026", "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1351257889596461059", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 19, "username": "robinalexander_", "id": "464694427"}, {"start": 75, "end": 80, "username": "welt", "id": "8720562"}]}, "conversation_id": "1351257889596461059", "referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1351256167893389313"}], "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-18T19:59:20.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 74, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "source": "Twitter Web App", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "\u201eDem neuen Parteivorsitzenden Armin #Laschet habe ich aber angeboten, in die jetzige #Bundesregierung einzutreten und das Bundeswirtschaftsministerium zu \u00fcbernehmen.\u201c (tm) #wegenmorgen #cdupt21 @reuters_de", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 36, "end": 44, "tag": "Laschet"}, {"start": 85, "end": 101, "tag": "Bundesregierung"}, {"start": 172, "end": 184, "tag": "wegenmorgen"}, {"start": 185, "end": 193, "tag": "cdupt21"}], "mentions": [{"start": 194, "end": 205, "username": "reuters_de", "id": "55035997"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350438086589763594", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350437813951623172", "referenced_tweets": [{"type": "replied_to", "id": "1350437813951623172"}], "lang": "de", "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "46", "name": "Brand Category", "description": "Categories within Brand Verticals that narrow down the scope of Brands"}, "entity": {"id": "781974596157181956", "name": "Online Site"}}, {"domain": {"id": "47", "name": "Brand", "description": "Brands and Companies"}, "entity": {"id": "10047963346", "name": "Reuters", "description": "Reuters"}}], "created_at": "2021-01-16T13:41:44.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 153, "reply_count": 1986, "like_count": 1647, "quote_count": 1153}, "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "in_reply_to_user_id": "1059395748289232896"}, {"text": "Die #CDU kann nicht nur von M\u00e4nnern aus #NRW gef\u00fchrt werden. Ins Pr\u00e4sidium w\u00e4ren bei meiner Bewerbung noch weniger #Frauen gew\u00e4hlt worden. Ich habe mich deshalb entschlossen, zugunsten der Frauen auf eine Kandidatur zu verzichten.\" (tm) #cdupt21 https://t.co/Y9Sm5PqdFm", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 4, "end": 8, "tag": "CDU"}, {"start": 40, "end": 44, "tag": "NRW"}, {"start": 115, "end": 122, "tag": "Frauen"}, {"start": 237, "end": 245, "tag": "cdupt21"}], "urls": [{"start": 246, "end": 269, "url": "https://t.co/Y9Sm5PqdFm", "expanded_url": "https://www.deutschlandfunk.de/cdu-merz-will-bundeswirtschaftsminister-werden.1939.de.html?drn:news_id=1216808", "display_url": "deutschlandfunk.de/cdu-merz-will-\u2026"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350437813951623172", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350437813951623172", "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-16T13:40:39.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 124, "reply_count": 1143, "like_count": 1354, "quote_count": 577}, "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "Ich gratuliere dem neuen #CDU-Vorsitzenden @ArminLaschet und m\u00f6chte Mitgliedern und Delegierten herzlich f\u00fcr die Unterst\u00fctzung danken. Jetzt kommt es darauf an, dass wir alle gemeinsam im Team arbeiten f\u00fcr eine moderne und erkennbare CDU, die begeistert und Wahlen gewinnt. (FM)", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 25, "end": 29, "tag": "CDU"}], "mentions": [{"start": 43, "end": 56, "username": "ArminLaschet", "id": "835541664"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350391855733747714", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350391855733747714", "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-16T10:38:02.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 166, "reply_count": 1183, "like_count": 3026, "quote_count": 159}, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "Mit mir wird es keine Zusammenarbeit mit der #AfD geben. Die W\u00e4hlerinnen und W\u00e4hler m\u00fcssen wissen: Eine Stimme f\u00fcr die AfD ist eine halbe Stimme f\u00fcr Rot-Rot-Gr\u00fcn. (tm) #Merz #TeamMerz #cdupt21", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 45, "end": 49, "tag": "AfD"}, {"start": 168, "end": 173, "tag": "Merz"}, {"start": 174, "end": 183, "tag": "TeamMerz"}, {"start": 184, "end": 192, "tag": "cdupt21"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350371496779255813", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350371496779255813", "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-16T09:17:08.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 131, "reply_count": 1270, "like_count": 1479, "quote_count": 473}, "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "\u201eIch wei\u00df, dass wir in der Frauenpolitik besser werden und mehr tun m\u00fcssen. Aber wenn ich wirklich ein \u201aFrauenproblem\u2018 h\u00e4tte, wie manche sagen, dann h\u00e4tten mir meine T\u00f6chter l\u00e4ngst die gelbe Karte gezeigt \u2013 und meine Frau h\u00e4tte mich nicht vor 40 Jahren geheiratet.\u201c (tm) #cdupt21", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 271, "end": 279, "tag": "cdupt21"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350370929487056897", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350370929487056897", "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-16T09:14:52.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 102, "reply_count": 1361, "like_count": 1810, "quote_count": 1122}, "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "Konsens und Kompromiss, Ma\u00df und Mitte halten \u2013 wie macht man das? Die Antwort gibt es nicht im Lehrbuch, sondern in einer Demokratie muss darum gerungen werden. Mit Leidenschaft! Wir m\u00fcssen den Meinungsstreit in die politische Mitte zur\u00fcckholen. (tm) #cdupt21 #wegenmorgen", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 251, "end": 259, "tag": "cdupt21"}, {"start": 260, "end": 272, "tag": "wegenmorgen"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350370214916059136", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350370214916059136", "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-16T09:12:02.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 44, "reply_count": 73, "like_count": 427, "quote_count": 13}, "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "Nicht Angst und Verzagtheit, sondern Mut und Zuversicht sind angebracht. Die Welt geht morgen nicht unter. Ob #Klimawandel oder #COVID19 \u2013 wir werden all diese Probleme nicht gegen das System, sondern mit ihm, mit Freiheit und Sozialer Marktwirtschaft l\u00f6sen! (tm) #wegenmorgen", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 110, "end": 122, "tag": "Klimawandel"}, {"start": 128, "end": 136, "tag": "COVID19"}, {"start": 264, "end": 276, "tag": "wegenmorgen"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350369621497573376", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350369621497573376", "lang": "de", "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "created_at": "2021-01-16T09:09:41.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 56, "reply_count": 131, "like_count": 673, "quote_count": 35}, "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "In einem Jahr haben wir wahrscheinlich bereits eine neue Bundesregierung. Wir als #CDU sind entschlossen, sie auch wieder anzuf\u00fchren. Die Mannschaft, die wir heute w\u00e4hlen \u2013 nicht der Vorsitzende allein \u2013 wird die Bundesrepublik Deutschland f\u00fcr viele Jahr pr\u00e4gen. (tm) #wegenmorgen", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 82, "end": 86, "tag": "CDU"}, {"start": 268, "end": 280, "tag": "wegenmorgen"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350368840094543873", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350368840094543873", "lang": "de", "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "12", "name": "Sports Team", "description": "A sports team organization, like Arsenal and the Boston Celtics"}, "entity": {"id": "731226244096741376", "name": "Germany"}}], "created_at": "2021-01-16T09:06:34.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 19, "reply_count": 51, "like_count": 275, "quote_count": 11}, "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "Die erste Botschaft lautet: Das ist #Digitalisierung. So geht CDU. Wir gehen mit gutem Beispiel voran und setzen die Standards, an denen sich alle anderen Parteien orientieren. (tm) #cdupt21 #TeamMerz #wegenmorgen", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 36, "end": 52, "tag": "Digitalisierung"}, {"start": 182, "end": 190, "tag": "cdupt21"}, {"start": 191, "end": 200, "tag": "TeamMerz"}, {"start": 201, "end": 213, "tag": "wegenmorgen"}]}, "reply_settings": "everyone", "id": "1350368591602999297", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "conversation_id": "1350368591602999297", "lang": "de", "created_at": "2021-01-16T09:05:35.000Z", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 25, "reply_count": 116, "like_count": 387, "quote_count": 24}, "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false}, {"text": "Guten Morgen vom Messegel\u00e4nde in Berlin. Gleich geht es los. Verfolgen Sie den ersten digitalen #CDU-Parteitag unserer Geschichte live \u00fcber alle Kan\u00e4le. Ich freue mich auf Sie und Ihre Unterst\u00fctzung. (FM) https://t.co/pV5pGDTakP", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 96, "end": 100, "tag": "CDU"}], "urls": [{"start": 205, "end": 228, "url": "https://t.co/pV5pGDTakP", "expanded_url":