, "end": 141, "url": "https://t.co/SAsSwAiDu9", "expanded_url": "https://www.ardmediathek.de/daserste/video/anne-will/wie-wollen-wir-leben-anne-will-zum-auftakt-der-ard-themenwoche/das-erste/Y3JpZDovL25kci5kZS9kNGVhMjFmNS1jNTZhLTRiZWMtYTBiOS0yZjlmN2Y5NGNmN2Y/", "display_url": "ardmediathek.de/daserste/video\u2026"}]}, "text": "Sendung verpasst? Hier k\u00f6nnen Sie die Diskussion bei #AnneWill mit Friedrich #Merz in der ARD-Mediathek ansehen. (tm)\nhttps://t.co/SAsSwAiDu9", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 14, "reply_count": 135, "like_count": 303, "quote_count": 15}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-15T21:42:34.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1328091045805121538", "id": "1328091045805121538", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 0, "end": 6, "tag": "China"}, {"start": 37, "end": 53, "tag": "Freihandelszone"}, {"start": 234, "end": 243, "tag": "AnneWill"}, {"start": 244, "end": 249, "tag": "Merz"}]}, "text": "#China hat heute die weltweit gr\u00f6\u00dfte #Freihandelszone der Welt auf die Beine gestellt und wir diskutieren hier ernsthaft \u00fcber korrektes Gendern in Gesetzesentw\u00fcrfen? Wir k\u00f6nnen doch die Welt um uns herum nicht v\u00f6llig ausblenden! (tm) #AnneWill #Merz", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 908, "reply_count": 1458, "like_count": 8628, "quote_count": 633}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-15T21:26:40.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1328087043285671941", "id": "1328087043285671941", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 226, "end": 235, "tag": "AnneWill"}, {"start": 236, "end": 241, "tag": "Merz"}, {"start": 242, "end": 257, "tag": "ARDThemenwoche"}]}, "text": "Der Bundeshaushalt gibt es schon heute her, in Infrastruktur oder die Netze zu investieren. Steuererh\u00f6hungen w\u00e4ren Gift f\u00fcr die Konjunktur und unsere Unternehmen. Es geht darum, dass wir die richtigen Priorit\u00e4ten setzen. (tm) #AnneWill #Merz #ARDThemenwoche", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 35, "reply_count": 52, "like_count": 698, "quote_count": 7}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "65", "name": "Interests and Hobbies Vertical", "description": "Top level interests and hobbies groupings, like Food or Travel"}, "entity": {"id": "781974596148793345", "name": "Business & finance"}}, {"domain": {"id": "66", "name": "Interests and Hobbies Category", "description": "A grouping of interests and hobbies entities, like Novelty Food or Destinations"}, "entity": {"id": "847888632711061504", "name": "Personal finance", "description": "Personal finance"}}, {"domain": {"id": "67", "name": "Interests and Hobbies", "description": "Interests, opinions, and behaviors of individuals, groups, or cultures; like Speciality Cooking or Theme Parks"}, "entity": {"id": "847894353708068864", "name": "Investing", "description": "Investing"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "replied_to", "id": "1328084408075771907"}], "created_at": "2020-11-15T21:20:09.000Z", "in_reply_to_user_id": "1059395748289232896", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1328084408075771907", "id": "1328085402549448706", "text": "(tm)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 1, "reply_count": 4, "like_count": 66, "quote_count": 3}, "lang": "und"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-15T21:16:12.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1328084408075771907", "id": "1328084408075771907", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 4, "end": 9, "tag": "Soli"}, {"start": 271, "end": 280, "tag": "AnneWill"}]}, "text": "Der #Soli war gedacht zur Refinanzierung der deutschen Einheit und ist Ende 2019 ausgelaufen. Es w\u00e4re ein Gebot der Fairness denen gegen\u00fcber gewesen, die 30 Jahre lang gezahlt haben, ihn f\u00fcr alle abzuschaffen. Jetzt muss das Bundesverfassungsgericht dar\u00fcber entscheiden. #AnneWill", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 84, "reply_count": 79, "like_count": 1458, "quote_count": 13}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-15T21:09:42.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1328082774843076609", "id": "1328082774843076609", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 80, "end": 87, "tag": "Europa"}, {"start": 125, "end": 132, "tag": "Gr\u00fcnen"}, {"start": 259, "end": 268, "tag": "AnneWill"}, {"start": 269, "end": 274, "tag": "Merz"}]}, "text": "Wir haben heute schon die h\u00f6chste Abgabenlast und die h\u00f6chsten Energiepreise in #Europa. Weiteres Schuldenmachen, wie es die #Gr\u00fcnen fordern, ist keine besonders fantasievolle Politik. Wir m\u00fcssen nach der Krise wieder zu soliden Haushalten zur\u00fcckkehren. (tm) #AnneWill #Merz", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 111, "reply_count": 136, "like_count": 1731, "quote_count": 31}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-15T21:02:34.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1328080980385599489", "id": "1328080980385599489", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 134, "end": 141, "tag": "Corona"}, {"start": 142, "end": 151, "tag": "AnneWill"}]}, "text": "Wir m\u00fcssen aufpassen, in der Bev\u00f6lkerung nicht die Erwartung zu wecken, dass wir nun alles aus den Staatskassen abfedern k\u00f6nnen. (tm) #Corona #AnneWill", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 84, "reply_count": 499, "like_count": 1810, "quote_count": 128}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-15T14:41:38.000Z", "source": "Twitter Web App", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1327985111988645893", "id": "1327985111988645893", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 61, "end": 70, "tag": "AnneWill"}, {"start": 117, "end": 124, "tag": "Corona"}], "mentions": [{"start": 75, "end": 85, "username": "ABaerbock", "id": "1469264387512979461"}, {"start": 90, "end": 101, "username": "OlafScholz", "id": "38150247"}], "urls": [{"start": 254, "end": 277, "url": "https://t.co/gpFIBLSMkK", "expanded_url": "https://daserste.ndr.de/annewill/archiv/Wie-wollen-wir-leben-ANNE-WILL-zum-Auftakt-der-ARD-Themenwoche-,themenwoche350.html", "display_url": "daserste.ndr.de/annewill/archi\u2026"}]}, "text": "Wie wollen wir leben? Dar\u00fcber diskutiere ich heute Abend bei #AnneWill mit @ABaerbock und @OlafScholz. Auch wenn uns #Corona im Augenblick in Atem h\u00e4lt, m\u00fcssen wir Vorstellungen dar\u00fcber haben, wie sich die Welt in den n\u00e4chsten 10 Jahren entwickelt. (FM) https://t.co/gpFIBLSMkK", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 19, "reply_count": 206, "like_count": 312, "quote_count": 38}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-14T11:36:59.000Z", "source": "Twitter Web App", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1327576256758632448", "id": "1327576256758632448", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 224, "end": 233, "tag": "wtag2020"}], "mentions": [{"start": 78, "end": 93, "username": "Wirtschaftsrat", "id": "2524572368"}], "urls": [{"start": 234, "end": 257, "url": "https://t.co/JTilBtEnaI", "expanded_url": "https://wirtschaftstag.wirtschaftsrat.de/", "display_url": "wirtschaftstag.wirtschaftsrat.de"}]}, "text": "Ich freue mich auf gute Diskussionen beim ersten digitalen Wirtschaftstag des @wirtschaftsrat|es am kommenden Montag. Der Livestream ist ab 9 Uhr auf der Veranstaltungsseite frei zug\u00e4nglich, schauen Sie gerne mal rein. (FM) #wtag2020\nhttps://t.co/JTilBtEnaI", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 12, "reply_count": 19, "like_count": 187, "quote_count": 6}, "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1326565423249305602"}], "created_at": "2020-11-12T17:17:35.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1326937194553094145", "id": "1326937194553094145", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 79, "end": 88, "tag": "WieLeben"}], "mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 16, "username": "AnneWillTalk", "id": "359982860"}, {"start": 109, "end": 120, "username": "OlafScholz", "id": "38150247"}, {"start": 122, "end": 132, "username": "ABaerbock", "id": "1469264387512979461"}]}, "text": "RT @AnneWillTalk: Wie wollen wir leben? \u00dcber die Leitfrage der ARD-Themenwoche #WieLeben diskutieren wir mit @OlafScholz, @ABaerbock und @_\u2026", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 18, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-11T12:17:50.000Z", "source": "Twitter Web App", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1326499373480546311", "id": "1326499373480546311", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 129, "end": 140, "tag": "Quarant\u00e4ne"}]}, "text": "Heute Morgen zweiter Schnelltest in dieser Woche, Ergebnis wieder negativ. Das Gesundheitsamt des Hochsauerlandkreises hat meine #Quarant\u00e4ne ab sofort aufgehoben. Ein sch\u00f6nes Geburtstagsgeschenk. Ganz herzlichen Dank auch an alle, die mir gratuliert haben! (FM)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 31, "reply_count": 176, "like_count": 1448, "quote_count": 26}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "replied_to", "id": "1325870440330506241"}], "created_at": "2020-11-09T18:39:27.000Z", "in_reply_to_user_id": "1059395748289232896", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1325870440330506241", "id": "1325870636368076800", "text": "Wir denken aber auch dankbar an den 9. November 1989, den Tag des Mauerfalls. Unsere Geschichte verl\u00e4sst uns nie, im Guten wie im Schlechten. (FM) 2/2", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 6, "reply_count": 17, "like_count": 301, "quote_count": 1}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-09T18:38:41.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1325870440330506241", "id": "1325870440330506241", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 4, "end": 14, "tag": "9November"}]}, "text": "Der #9November ist ein besonderer Tag in unserer Geschichte. Wir denken still und besch\u00e4mt an den 9. November 1938 und die \u00dcbergriffe der Nationalsozialisten auf j\u00fcdische Mitb\u00fcrger. (FM) 1/2", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 18, "reply_count": 33, "like_count": 376, "quote_count": 5}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-09T13:20:26.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1325790349642649603", "id": "1325790349642649603", "text": "Trotz Antik\u00f6rper und neg. Schnelltest bin ich seit heute leider wieder in Quarant\u00e4ne. Ausl\u00f6ser ist eine Begegnung mit dem Staatsminister f\u00fcr Regionalentwicklung Thomas Schmidt am letzten Freitag in Sachsen, der mittlerweile erkrankt ist. Ich w\u00fcnsche ihm schnelle Genesung! (FM)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 46, "reply_count": 207, "like_count": 834, "quote_count": 45}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2020-11-09T09:48:09.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1325736930617794560", "id": "1325736930617794560", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 73, "end": 79, "tag": "Biden"}, {"start": 89, "end": 97, "tag": "Amerika"}, {"start": 122, "end": 128, "tag": "Trump"}], "urls": [{"start": 252, "end": 275, "url": "https://t.co/lnpSC6HqiA", "expanded_url": "https://www.focus.de/politik/ausland/us-wahl/u-s-wah-l-amerika-ist-kein-vorbild-mehr_id_12628513.html", "display_url": "focus.de/politik/auslan\u2026"}]}, "text": "\u201eIch habe mir nie die Illusion gemacht, dass alles wieder gut wird, wenn #Biden gewinnt. #Amerika hat sich ver\u00e4ndert, und #Trump ist im Grunde nur ein Ausdruck dieser Ver\u00e4nderung. Aber mit Biden kann man nat\u00fcrlich konstruktiver zusammenarbeiten.\u201c (tm)\nhttps://t.co/lnpSC6HqiA", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 27, "reply_count": 108, "like_count": 330, "quote_count": 12}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "799022225751871488", "name": "Donald Trump", "description": "US President Donald Trump"}}, {"domain": {"id": "35", "name": "Politician", "description": "Politicians in the world, like Joe Biden"}, "entity": {"id": "799022225751871488", "name": "Donald Trump", "description": "US President Donald Trump"}}, {"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "10040395078", "nam