{"http_status": 200, "account_name": "_FriedrichMerz", "account_data": {"Name": "Merz, Friedrich", "Partei": "CDU", "id": 1059395748289232896, "screen_name": "_FriedrichMerz", "t0": "20211020-103923.json", "value": "Merz, Friedrich"}, "params": [["query", "from:_FriedrichMerz"], ["max_results", "100"], ["start_time", "2007-01-01T00:00:00Z"], ["end_time", "2022-04-18T11:59:59Z"], ["tweet.fields", "attachments,author_id,context_annotations,conversation_id,created_at,entities,geo,id,in_reply_to_user_id,lang,possibly_sensitive,public_metrics,referenced_tweets,reply_settings,source,text,withheld"], ["expansions", "author_id,referenced_tweets.id,referenced_tweets.id.author_id,entities.mentions.username,attachments.poll_ids,attachments.media_keys,in_reply_to_user_id,geo.place_id"], ["media.fields", "duration_ms,height,media_key,preview_image_url,public_metrics,type,url,width"], ["place.fields", "contained_within,country,country_code,full_name,geo,id,name,place_type"], ["poll.fields", "duration_minutes,end_datetime,id,options,voting_status"], ["user.fields", "created_at,description,entities,id,location,name,pinned_tweet_id,profile_image_url,protected,public_metrics,url,username,verified,withheld"], ["next_token", "b26v89c19zqg8o3fos8t7nfiugc95lvtm7purga3qhabh"]], "response": {"data": [{"conversation_id": "1312309634217250816", "created_at": "2020-10-03T08:35:14.000Z", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "id": "1312310228336115715", "referenced_tweets": [{"type": "replied_to", "id": "1312309634217250816"}], "text": "Aus westdeutscher Sicht kann ich nur dazu raten, einander zuzuh\u00f6ren und Empathie zu zeigen. Wir d\u00fcrfen in Dankbarkeit auf das zur\u00fcckblicken, was wir in den letzten 30 Jahren gemeinsam erreicht haben. Ich w\u00fcnsche Ihnen ein sch\u00f6nes Feiertagswochenende! (FM) #einheit30", "reply_settings": "everyone", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 8, "reply_count": 17, "like_count": 199, "quote_count": 4}, "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 256, "end": 266, "tag": "einheit30"}]}, "in_reply_to_user_id": "1059395748289232896", "lang": "de"}, {"conversation_id": "1312309634217250816", "created_at": "2020-10-03T08:32:52.000Z", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "id": "1312309634217250816", "text": "Seit 30 Jahren leben wir in Frieden und #Freiheit im wiedervereinigten #Deutschland. Ich bin viel in Ostdeutschland unterwegs, ich mag diesen Teil unseres Landes und seine Menschen wirklich sehr. Viel ist gelungen, viel ist noch zu tun. (FM) #TagderDeutschenEinheit", "reply_settings": "everyone", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 34, "reply_count": 76, "like_count": 443, "quote_count": 4}, "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 40, "end": 49, "tag": "Freiheit"}, {"start": 71, "end": 83, "tag": "Deutschland"}, {"start": 242, "end": 265, "tag": "TagderDeutschenEinheit"}]}, "lang": "de"}, {"conversation_id": "1312021709843828738", "created_at": "2020-10-02T13:28:46.000Z", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck", "id": "1312021709843828738", "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 271, "end": 276, "username": "welt", "id": "8720562"}], "hashtags": [{"start": 5, "end": 21, "tag": "Bundeskanzlerin"}, {"start": 134, "end": 141, "tag": "Corona"}]}, "text": "\u201eDie #Bundeskanzlerin handelt, wie ich finde, richtig wenn sie die Menschen wie in dieser Woche darum bittet, etwas mehr aufzupassen. #Corona ist nicht vorbei, wir sind m\u00f6glicherweise mitten in einer zweiten Welle und es gibt \u00fcberhaupt keinen Grund f\u00fcr Entwarnung.\u201c (tm) @welt", "reply_settings": "everyone", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 33, "reply_count": 265, "like_count": 429, "quote_count": 39}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"conversation_id": "1311991967799283712", "created_at": "2020-10-02T11:30:35.000Z", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "TweetDeck", "id": "1311991967799283712", "text": "\u201eEs ist fast eine Ironie der Geschichte, dass #Trump, der #Corona am l\u00e4ngsten geleugnet hat, nun selbst betroffen ist. Trotz aller Meinungsverschiedenheiten, auch in Stil und Umgang, w\u00fcnsche ich ihm und seiner Frau gute Besserung.\u201c (tm) #TrumpHasCorona https://t.co/MXghwswctN", "reply_settings": "everyone", "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 37, "reply_count": 255, "like_count": 539, "quote_count": 46}, "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 46, "end": 52, "tag": "Trump"}, {"start": 58, "end": 65, "tag": "Corona"}, {"start": 237, "end": 252, "tag": "TrumpHasCorona"}], "urls": [{"start": 253, "end": 276, "url": "https://t.co/MXghwswctN", "expanded_url": "https://www.welt.de/politik/deutschland/plus217029956/Friedrich-Merz-Demokratische-Parteien-muessen-koalitionsfaehig-sein-die-Gruenen-gehoeren-dazu.html", "display_url": "welt.de/politik/deutsc\u2026"}]}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "799022225751871488", "name": "Donald Trump", "description": "US President Donald Trump"}}, {"domain": {"id": "35", "name": "Politician", "description": "Politicians in the world, like Joe Biden"}, "entity": {"id": "799022225751871488", "name": "Donald Trump", "description": "US President Donald Trump"}}, {"domain": {"id": "123", "name": "Ongoing News Story", "description": "Ongoing News Stories like 'Brexit'"}, "entity": {"id": "1220701888179359745", "name": "COVID-19"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"conversation_id": "1310513464553754626", "created_at": "2020-09-28T09:35:32.000Z", "possibly_sensitive": false, "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "id": "1310513464553754626", "referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "131050931517905