 "conversation_id": "1135857646555291649", "id": "1135857646555291649", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 256, "end": 263, "tag": "wtag19"}, {"start": 264, "end": 269, "tag": "wrat"}], "mentions": [{"start": 93, "end": 108, "username": "Wirtschaftsrat", "id": "2524572368"}], "urls": [{"start": 270, "end": 293, "url": "https://t.co/uRoRIQWZgd", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1135857646555291649/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/uRoRIQWZgd"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1135857266949836800"]}, "text": "Ich danke der Bundesdelegiertenversammlung f\u00fcr das Vertrauen und freue mich sehr darauf, den @wirtschaftsrat als Vizepr\u00e4sident unter der F\u00fchrung von Astrid Hamker in seiner wichtigen Funktion als Gewissen der Sozialen Marktwirtschaft zu unterst\u00fctzen. (FM) #wtag19 #wrat https://t.co/uRoRIQWZgd", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 36, "reply_count": 18, "like_count": 264, "quote_count": 6}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2019-06-03T17:29:00.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1135599277508632576", "id": "1135599277508632576", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 135, "end": 142, "tag": "wtag19"}, {"start": 143, "end": 148, "tag": "wrat"}]}, "text": "Morgen Abend hier exklusiv im Livestream: Friedrich Merz spricht ab ca. 19:30 Uhr beim Wirtschaftstag 2019. Schauen Sie doch mal rein. #wtag19 #wrat (TeamFM)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 12, "reply_count": 10, "like_count": 157, "quote_count": 1}, "lang": "de"}, {"referenced_tweets": [{"type": "retweeted", "id": "1135515719574183937"}], "created_at": "2019-06-03T12:16:54.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1135520732295966720", "id": "1135520732295966720", "text": "RT @realArminPeter: Morgen kandidiert @_FriedrichMerz auf dem Wirtschaftstag 2019 in Berlin als Vizepr\u00e4sident des @wirtschaftsrat|es. #wtag\u2026", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 6, "reply_count": 0, "like_count": 0, "quote_count": 0}, "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 3, "end": 18, "username": "realArminPeter", "id": "1105414883758231552"}, {"start": 38, "end": 53, "username": "_FriedrichMerz", "id": "1059395748289232896"}, {"start": 114, "end": 129, "username": "Wirtschaftsrat", "id": "2524572368"}]}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "10", "name": "Person", "description": "Named people in the world like Nelson Mandela"}, "entity": {"id": "887730612060082176", "name": "Andreas Scheuer", "description": "Andreas Scheuer"}}, {"domain": {"id": "13", "name": "Place", "description": "Named places in the world, like Fenway Park"}, "entity": {"id": "855409238318882816", "name": "Europe", "description": "Europa"}}, {"domain": {"id": "13", "name": "Place", "description": "Named places in the world, like Fenway Park"}, "entity": {"id": "855410081906556930", "name": "Germany", "description": "Germany"}}, {"domain": {"id": "13", "name": "Place", "description": "Named places in the world, like Fenway Park"}, "entity": {"id": "855410510082080770", "name": "Berlin", "description": "Berlin"}}, {"domain": {"id": "35", "name": "Politician", "description": "Politicians in the world, like Joe Biden"}, "entity": {"id": "887730612060082176", "name": "Andreas Scheuer", "description": "Andreas Scheuer"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2019-05-31T16:14:27.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1134493353368834048", "id": "1134493353368834048", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 78, "end": 93, "tag": "Nachhaltigkeit"}], "urls": [{"start": 103, "end": 126, "url": "https://t.co/0hMiVTyGbW", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1134493353368834048/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/0hMiVTyGbW"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1134493055917182976"]}, "text": "Unbezahlbare soziale Versprechen zulasten der J\u00fcngeren sind unverantwortlich. #Nachhaltigkeit (TeamFM) https://t.co/0hMiVTyGbW", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 56, "reply_count": 59, "like_count": 411, "quote_count": 20}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2019-05-31T08:40:56.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1134379221353193472", "id": "1134379221353193472", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 19, "end": 36, "tag": "FridaysForFuture"}, {"start": 174, "end": 178, "tag": "CO2"}, {"start": 254, "end": 264, "tag": "Interview"}], "mentions": [{"start": 269, "end": 278, "username": "StZ_NEWS", "id": "18552451"}]}, "text": "Man kann nicht wie #FridaysForFuture sagen: Wir schalten alles ab und verbieten individuelle Mobilit\u00e4t. Stattdessen m\u00fcssen wir technologieoffen und ohne Panik m\u00f6glichst viel #CO2 zu den geringsten Belastungen f\u00fcr B\u00fcrger und Unternehmen einsparen. (FM im #Interview mit @StZ_NEWS)", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 246, "reply_count": 979, "like_count": 1482, "quote_count": 282}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2019-05-28T16:00:00.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1133402551360151553", "id": "1133402551360151553", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 12, "end": 23, "tag": "Europawahl"}, {"start": 76, "end": 91, "tag": "Klimakanzlerin"}], "mentions": [{"start": 38, "end": 42, "username": "CDU", "id": "20429858"}], "urls": [{"start": 280, "end": 303, "url": "https://t.co/47O1AH1cKF", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1133402551360151553/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/47O1AH1cKF"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1133388184241487880"]}, "text": "Nach dieser #Europawahl muss sich die @CDU fragen, warum wir nach 14 Jahren #Klimakanzlerin unsere Klimaziele verfehlen, Haushalte und Unternehmen mit den h\u00f6chsten Strompreisen Europas belasten und die strategische und kulturelle Kontrolle \u00fcber das Thema verloren haben. (TeamFM) https://t.co/47O1AH1cKF", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 750, "reply_count": 717, "like_count": 3316, "quote_count": 385}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2019-05-25T16:02:12.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1132315942220947456", "id": "1132315942220947456", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 195, "end": 210, "tag": "Europawahl2019"}], "urls": [{"start": 278, "end": 301, "url": "https://t.co/c4bzqIxWWT", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1132315942220947456/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/c4bzqIxWWT"}]}, "attachments": {"media_keys": ["3_1132315819717877762"]}, "text": "Wir sind Zeitzeugen historischer Ver\u00e4nderungen und stehen mehr denn je in einer Verantwortung, die \u00fcber unser Land hinausgeht. Europa kann nur gemeinsam etwas bewegen. Setzen wir deshalb bei der #Europawahl2019 ein Signal f\u00fcr ein freies, starkes und demokratisches Europa! (FM) https://t.co/c4bzqIxWWT", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 27, "reply_count": 31, "like_count": 157, "quote_count": 1}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "29", "name": "Events [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service related Events domain"}, "entity": {"id": "1093951580871614464", "name": "European elections", "description": "European elections"}}, {"domain": {"id": "38", "name": "Political Race", "description": ""}, "entity": {"id": "1093951580871614464", "name": "European elections", "description": "European elections"}}, {"domain": {"id": "13", "name": "Place", "description": "Named places in the world, like Fenway Park"}, "entity": {"id": "855409238318882816", "name": "Europe", "description": "Europa"}}, {"domain": {"id": "29", "name": "Events [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service related Events domain"}, "entity": {"id": "1130792428074483712", "name": "Elecciones al Parlamento Europeo", "description": "Adem\u00e1s de las elecciones municipales y auton\u00f3micas, los espa\u00f1oles est\u00e1n llamados a votar en los comicios europeos que se celebran el 26 de mayo. Los ciudadanos elegir\u00e1n a los 751 miembros del Parlamento Europeo, de los cuales 54 ser\u00e1n elegidos por Espa\u00f1a.\n\nFoto via @InfobaeTecno"}}, {"domain": {"id": "29", "name": "Events [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service related Events domain"}, "entity": {"id": "1131548654135734272", "name": "European Union Elections 2019", "description": "Stay updated as the results come in for the European Elections.\n\nPhoto via: @ASInvestmentsUK"}}], "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2019-05-20T09:13:57.000Z", "source": "TweetDeck", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1130401260576935936", "id": "1130401260576935936", "entities": {"hashtags": [{"start": 229, "end": 240, "tag": "Europawahl"}], "urls": [{"start": 241, "end": 264, "url": "https://t.co/vo4DXFE7Vj", "expanded_url": "https://www.thueringer-allgemeine.de/web/zgt/politik/detail/-/specific/Thueringen-droht-ab-Herbst-die-Regierungsunfaehigkeit-Interview-mit-Friedrich-M-1098807408?utm_medium=Social&utm_campaign=Echobox&utm_source=Facebook&fbclid=IwAR1oNdZ1KIRXumvmD9pKNKRmYGnNZIJN7taq6Q55oSSqt7e9OZfK9Ok-JuE#Echobox=1558325882", "display_url": "thueringer-allgemeine.de/web/zgt/politi\u2026"}]}, "text": "\u201eDie AfD ist kein Koalitionspartner f\u00fcr irgendeine b\u00fcrgerliche Partei in Deutschland. Wenn Extremisten und Nationalisten an f\u00fchrender Stelle t\u00e4tig sind, dann ist das eine rote Linie, die wir nicht \u00fcberschreiten d\u00fcrfen\u201c. (TeamFM) #Europawahl https://t.co/vo4DXFE7Vj", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 47, "reply_count": 58, "like_count