 auf @ntvde mit @louisklamroth \u00fcber die @CDU, meinen pers\u00f6nlichen Werdegang und \u00fcber aktuelle politische Themen. Schauen Sie doch mal rein. (FM) https://t.co/Nv3goKNrWS", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 19, "reply_count": 17, "like_count": 127, "quote_count": 4}, "entities": {"mentions": [{"start": 41, "end": 47, "username": "ntvde", "id": "19232587"}, {"start": 52, "end": 66, "username": "louisklamroth", "id": "73939469"}, {"start": 76, "end": 80, "username": "CDU", "id": "20429858"}], "urls": [{"start": 181, "end": 204, "url": "https://t.co/Nv3goKNrWS", "expanded_url": "https://twitter.com/_FriedrichMerz/status/1125791519141711872/photo/1", "display_url": "pic.twitter.com/Nv3goKNrWS"}]}, "lang": "de"}, {"created_at": "2019-05-07T11:49:17.000Z", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "possibly_sensitive": false, "author_id": "1059395748289232896", "reply_settings": "everyone", "conversation_id": "1125729311116410882", "id": "1125729311116410882", "text": "Aus tiefer \u00dcberzeugung unterst\u00fctze ich den Aufruf der Nationalstiftung zur Europawahl: \u201eLiefern wir das Europ\u00e4ische Parlament nicht denen aus, die es abschaffen wollen. Setzen wir ein Signal f\u00fcr ein freies und starkes und demokratisches Europa\u201c. (FM) https://t.co/z7sfvQSxla", "public_metrics": {"retweet_count": 28, "reply_count": 14, "like_count": 204, "quote_count": 2}, "context_annotations": [{"domain": {"id": "29", "name": "Events [Entity Service]", "description": "Entity Service related Events domain"}, "entity": {"id": "1093951580871614464", "name": "European elections", "description": "European elections"}}, {"domain": {"id": "38", "name": "Political Race", "description": ""}, "entity": {"id": "1093951580871614464", "name": "European elections", "description": "European elections"}}, {"domain": {"id": "13", "name": "Place", "description": "Named places in the world, like Fenway Park"}, "entity": {"id": "855409238318882816", "name": "Europe", "description": "Europa"}}